cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.RO 

The paper focuses on 3D shape understanding from single and multiple images using a deep-learning architecture and loss function. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also introduces new synthetic datasets and demonstrates the use of the architecture on a benchmark dataset, which could fall under graphics (cs.GR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories.
